research_municipality_step.notes: Parsippany-Troy Hills Township operates under a Mayor-Council Plan E Faulkner Act form of government. Pulkit Desai was sworn in as Mayor on January 3, 2026, with his term ending December 31, 2029. The Township Council consists of five members elected at-large. Judy Hernandez, Matthew Kavanagh, and Diya Patel are current council members, along with Paul Carifi Jr. and Matt McGrath.
